fulltitle: Mark Crispin Miller, Media and Society
title: Mark Crispin Miller, Media and Society
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

Professor Miller talked about the negative influence of media mergers on citizens' resources for both entertainment and information. He took questions from the audience.
